### [MODIFY] [dashboard/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/frontend/src/app/(app)/dashboard/page.tsx)

- Remove "Hızlı İşlemler" section entirely
